title: FRIDAY 4/30 - NFL DRAFT DAY ONE
itunes:title: FRIDAY 4/30 - NFL DRAFT DAY ONE
description:
Quarterbacks dominating the draft on day one, going off the board with the first three picks with Trey Lance landing with the 49ers. Kyle Shanahan (0:31) talks about what happens next for Jimmy Garoppolo. The Bears trading up to land Justin Fields (1:30). He talks about what he brings to the Windy City. Aaron Rodgers (2:13) not happy in Green Bay, but will the team trade him? Plus, Rams GM Les Snead (2:50) tests positive for COVID-19
